<s> The 1.1 mechanism is not of use when 1. The server does not provide individual URLs for all the possible documents that could be returned when accessing a URL. 2. The server may have URLs for the individual documents, but does not return an exhaustive list of possibilities (maybe it would be too large) 3. The document returned depends on a parameter in a manner that cannot be described by a URI: header.  </s>
